---------------------------
Command: datasource offline
---------------------------
Description: Bring a single data source to offline state
Syntax: 
  datasource <host> offline
 
The 'datasource online' brings the host's data source offline and
makes it unavailable to applications.  It has no effect if the data
source is already offline.

Usage: 

The following command takes data source mercury offline. 

  datasource mercury offline 
